    h1 Button React Component
    ul.docs-index
    p Button React component represents Framework7's <a href="../docs/button.html">Button</a> elements.

    h2 Button Components
    p There are following components included:
    ul
      li <code><b>Button</b></code> / <code><b>F7Button</b></code> - single button
      li <code><b>Segmented</b></code> / <code><b>F7Segmented</b></code> - segmented wrapper for buttons

